:::Time Warp/Hun-Grr:::

::Time Warp runs to the battle, seeing Hun-Grr fighting::
Time Warp: Let's see how you take THIS!
::he opened fire at Hun-Grr.  Hun-Grr spins around::
Hun-Grr: You attack Hun-grr.  You DIE!
::He transformed to creature mode and bites Time Warp's gun hand off::
Time Warp: ahhhhhh!
Hun-grr: Now Hun-grr finish it!
::He opens his jaws and his left head sinks its teeth into Time Warp's side, 
while the right head bites Time Warp's head off.  Time Warp's mutalated body 
lay on the ground.  Hun-grr ate a bit of it, and then went back to the rest 
of the battle::
